item.title: Imposterdev
item.description: Why imposterdev? During my three years at the university I never ever attributed my own skills and effort as the reason behind good results. With every answer correct on an exam the felling of accomplishment was extremly short. Within minutes after getting the result, I had a strong feeling that the exam was to easy.
